{"id": 1173, "genre": 1001, "title": "对于各种文创产品，你有啥要吐槽的？", "description": "皇帝卖萌贴纸，三百块一个的插画马克杯，印着“洪荒之力”的开瓶器，什么的。（题图来自：Josh Holinaty）", "record_count": 2835, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160817172548tJdYap12rKg5DVkC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-19T03:05:13Z", "options": [{"id": 108800, "content": "一时的情动，一世的悲恸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607127}, {"id": 108801, "content": "你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722933}, {"id": 108802, "content": "不管是什么鞋上都印着   sport   ", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573378}, {"id": 110596, "content": "有些手工烧制的碗碟真的不是做坏的失败品？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679121}, {"id": 108805, "content": "做工粗糙，图案倒是时下泛滥", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686157}, {"id": 109061, "content": "五毛钱特效", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723875}, {"id": 108807, "content": "为了创意，丢掉美感", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141957}, {"id": 108808, "content": "粗制滥造，雷同太严重！缺少创意！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722986}, {"id": 272906, "content": "没有质感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267566}, {"id": 108810, "content": "价格和质量不成正比，这里的质量包含创意部分和产品部分", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114150}, {"id": 109066, "content": "抄袭创意的居多，用心做质量的是少数。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700503}, {"id": 108811, "content": "钱包为情怀买单，有钱随意", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722958}, {"id": 108812, "content": "这对喜欢无印风格的我来说显得有些多余。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722995}, {"id": 108813, "content": "只注重所谓的“概念”和“创意”，然而质量往往糟心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262225}, {"id": 120589, "content": "没个性\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631927}, {"id": 108814, "content": "一大多是一堆装X，让人视觉疲劳，缺乏温暖的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051422}, {"id": 108303, "content": "溢价非常高的家居用品，质量也就…", "image": null, "praise_count": 263, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 108304, "content": "千篇一律，哪儿都是“朕知道了”的胶带", "image": null, "praise_count": 113, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 108305, "content": "不走心，一件T恤上印两句过时流行语", "image": null, "praise_count": 475, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 108306, "content": "不实用，买个微缩版的青铜器能干嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 109586, "content": "啥玩意都可以说是\n纳米技术~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726009}, {"id": 108819, "content": "流行更新的太快，周边都赶不上了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723039}, {"id": 111123, "content": "贵！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734105}, {"id": 108821, "content": "感觉出来几周后就变成某宝爆款", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719425}, {"id": 109077, "content": " 。", "image": "img/option/option/20160820171052hUy2Qw4clWIveT6V.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724374}, {"id": 108823, "content": "口水文化，并不会长久", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719355}, {"id": 109079, "content": "就是买回去等过时等封尘等掉垃圾桶的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698262}, {"id": 109080, "content": "好奇心日报也算文创产品吧，有什么不好的呢？主要看形式和需求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724195}, {"id": 108826, "content": "创意要走心的，这些只是时代变迁的产物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723084}, {"id": 109082, "content": "漫展里卖的那种放一张漫画就卖得老贵的水杯?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690855}, {"id": 108827, "content": "烂大街", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529593}, {"id": 108828, "content": "虽说创意值钱  但并不值那么多", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723118}, {"id": 108830, "content": "就是打着文创原创伪商品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693977}, {"id": 108831, "content": "大多数为了骗钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619155}, {"id": 108832, "content": "并不是把图案直接印上去就叫文创的好吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115257}, {"id": 108833, "content": "一次性消费的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615678}, {"id": 109089, "content": "价格高", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 108834, "content": "大部分都是打着品牌的旗号卖的山寨货质量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722051}, {"id": 109090, "content": "脸花神虚，就遮住了气质", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722823}, {"id": 108835, "content": "所以文创产品是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302846}, {"id": 109091, "content": "大部分不值这个300的价，甚至五十我都觉得多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157298}, {"id": 108836, "content": "打错英文词语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719305}, {"id": 108837, "content": "说不出来哪里好，都知道over price，可还是忍不住会买", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723173}, {"id": 109861, "content": "根本没什么用处的东西，创意不足一毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486833}, {"id": 108838, "content": "没有美感，缺乏创意，不环保，过时快。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723181}, {"id": 108839, "content": "一夜情", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710036}, {"id": 108841, "content": "感觉还是DIY来得更实在", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719655}, {"id": 109097, "content": "潮流都是会过时的，真正有内涵才能持久下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723375}, {"id": 108842, "content": "真的是在卖情怀，而且大都是一些不大实用的精致玩意", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717057}, {"id": 109098, "content": "创意太垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724450}]}